       <div class="news-item">
        <h4 class="date">
         February 20, 2019
        </h4>
        <h5>
         <a href="https://safety-security.uchicago.edu/news/route_changes_due_to_construction">
          Route Changes due to Construction
         </a>
        </h5>
        <p>
         Due to construction, the CTA #172, East and Regents Express are being rerouted.
        </p>
        <p>
         <p>
         </p>
        </p>
       </div>
       <div class="news-item">
        <h4 class="date">
         January 18, 2019
        </h4>
        <h5>
         <a href="https://safety-security.uchicago.edu/news/mlk_holiday_shuttle_schedule1">
          MLK Holiday Shuttle Schedule
         </a>
        </h5>
        <p>
         Due to the Martin Luther King, Jr. holiday on Monday, January 21, 2019, the Polsky Express and 53rd Street Express shuttles will not operate.
        </p>
       </div>
       <div class="news-item">
        <h4 class="date">
         January 11, 2019
        </h4>
        <h5>
         <a href="https://safety-security.uchicago.edu/news/cta_arrival_predictions_now_available">
          CTA Arrival Predictions Now Available
         </a>
        </h5>
        <p>
         The TransLoc Rider (UChicago) App is now able to display the estimated arrival times for CTA bus routes that travel on or very close to campus.
        </p>
       </div>
